        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName><hi rend="print">Down, | Beckenham, Kent.</hi></placeName>
                    <date>Sept. 12<hi rend="superscript">th</hi></date>
                    <salute>Dear Sir</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>I am much obliged for your kindness in writing to me.— Facts rellating to the wonderful power of inheritance always have a special interest for me.—<ref target="#foot.f2"/></p>
<p>With sincere thanks, I remain Dear Sir | yours faithfully | Charles Darwin</p> 
                </div>
            </div>

            
            
            
